description: A `TableCell` based component for placing inside `TableFooter` for pagination.
propActionsComponent:
The component used for displaying the actions.
Either a string to use a HTML element or a component.
propBackIconButtonProps: Props applied to the back arrow [`IconButton`](/api/icon-button/) component.
propClasses: Override or extend the styles applied to the component.
propComponent:
The component used for the root node.
Either a string to use a HTML element or a component.
propCount:
The total number of rows.

To enable server side pagination for an unknown number of items, provide -1.
propGetItemAriaLabel:
Accepts a function which returns a string value that provides a user-friendly name for the current page.

For localization purposes, you can use the provided [translations](/guides/localization/).
propLabelDisplayedRows:
Customize the displayed rows label. Invoked with a `{ from, to, count, page }`
object.

For localization purposes, you can use the provided [translations](/guides/localization/).
propLabelRowsPerPage:
Customize the rows per page label.

For localization purposes, you can use the provided [translations](/guides/localization/).
propNextIconButtonProps: Props applied to the next arrow [`IconButton`](/api/icon-button/) element.
propOnPageChange: Callback fired when the page is changed.
propOnRowsPerPageChange: Callback fired when the number of rows per page is changed.
propPage: The zero-based index of the current page.
propRowsPerPage: The number of rows per page.
propRowsPerPageOptions:
Customizes the options of the rows per page select field. If less than two options are
available, no select field will be displayed.
propSelectProps: Props applied to the rows per page [`Select`](/api/select/) element.
stylesRoot: Styles applied to the root element.
stylesToolbar: Styles applied to the Toolbar component.
stylesSpacer: Styles applied to the spacer element.
stylesCaption: Styles applied to the caption Typography components if `variant="caption"`.
stylesSelectRoot: Styles applied to the Select component root element.
stylesSelect: Styles applied to the Select component `select` class.
stylesSelectIcon: Styles applied to the Select component `icon` class.
stylesMenuItem: Styles applied to the MenuItem component.
stylesActions: Styles applied to the internal `TablePaginationActions` component.
